        the CGI Servlet to mitigate <a href="https://httpoxy.org">httpoxy</a>
        (<a href="https://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2016-5388">CVE-2016-5388</a>) by default and to provide a mechanism that can be
